channel.title: Panopticlick - your fingerprint is nearly unique
channel.description: I'm running the default whonix without any third-party add-ons. But the eff website says my fingerprint is nearly unique when using the site with javascript. Is that something to be worried? some applications require javascript whether you like it or not.
